{"tid":1060112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇吸引力法則？","createTime":"2019-03-13T14:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T04:09:28.000Z","uid":164090,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1bff2c89502804fa03e7b530ffa065308f44704f","tid":1060112,"uid":164090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"前排睇完&ldquo;秘密&rdquo;，對佢所講既吸引力法則半信半疑。<br />\n<br />\n半疑者，覺得佢話乜&ldquo;思想係電波，射向宇宙，宇宙就會指派你想要既野俾你&ldquo;依類偽科學好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半信者，吸引力法則喺現實生活又錯唔哂，比如樂觀既人帶俾人歡樂，人地自然會對你好啲之類。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"74337cf3afb1aa169ec4b49b866040400213bf8e","tid":1060112,"uid":113912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"訓喇"},{"pid":"d4e78ea310244716b81090f71010d1c7952c196e","tid":1060112,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"起碼佢吸引咗你銀包先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45623126988504078c3fc16d4b3f7c1164fe425e","tid":1060112,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"你唔努力，點吸引你都唔會成功"},{"pid":"54a7a19bb64c196257210e862b9a55fc87962213","tid":1060112,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"信第三段"},{"pid":"49a6108d738f69820364b7ad8c4c43e7637f33ea","tid":1060112,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"044fba1913da1223a0130cc79b3e336e5a5a07e9","tid":1060112,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"606ea833cee2e75c051b5fbd288764309239d06c","tid":1060112,"uid":157516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"睇多啲不同類型既書，就會發現從心理學，腦科學潛意識都有類似吸引力法則既解說。<br />\n睇腦科學書，安多酚都係類似作用，當你諗得越多，就會越容易成真。<br />\n致富聖經，係走訪左八十個有錢人綜合出的致富方法，內容都係類似吸引力法則但非new age書。<br />\n<br />\n唔需要讖得太神化"},{"pid":"5ca8b45c92e96f8ced02d8c1b7ea64a6bced3da7","tid":1060112,"uid":227711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T03:19:38.000Z","msg":"全部都係new age,只係換個比較專門既terms啫，其中核心既思想都係一樣。<br />\n要你向&quot; 宇宙&quot;落訂單<br />\n極端啲講可以算係通靈既一種"},{"pid":"baa4ce44e4e642b13474b74297116bb278a3a24a","tid":1060112,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"心理作用"}]}